# [Interview #1150: Librarypalooza, Entry #18](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=1150#18)

#### Paladin Brewer

Can a kandra duplicate a parshendi carapace?

#### Brandon Sanderson

No, they cannot.
